trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.MobileControls.DeviceElement"></xref> objects.
For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.
The DeviceElementCollection class contains a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.DeviceElement> objects that are read from the configuration file.
For more information on the structure and contents of the configuration file, see [\<mobileControls>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/57d7cfd1-baf0-44bb-9b38-c438bc875839).
